
Dependencies:
  Scons
  Python (for SCons)
  SDL-devel
  SDL_gfx

ALL PLATFORMS:

1. Install SCons
2. Install SDL-devel (Windows users, see instructions below)
3. Bring up a command line, and enter the command 'scons'

WINDOWS BUILD:

Download the file SDL_deps.zip from http://cloud.github.com/downloads/andyfischer/circa/SDL_deps.zip

Unzip the contents into the 'circa' folder
